1951;;You Never Can Tell;;American;;Lou Breslow;;Dick Powell, Peggy Dow;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/You_Never_Can_Tell_(1951_film);;An ex-police dog named King inherits a fortune from his eccentric millionaire owner. But someone poisons him for his fortune, and he is able to go back to earth as a human detective named Rex Shepard to bring his killer to justice.